## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `flutter analyze` — zero errors across all modified files

### Manual Verification (User Testing)
1. Cancel appointment at time X → book different patient at time X → should NOT show warning
2. Book call-by for unique patient on future date → should NOT show warning
3. Fill patient details → card should show "Start Consultation" (not "Appointment Ended")
4. Click "Start Consultation" → should create consultation and navigate to form
5. Complete consultation → card should show "Appointment Ended"
